sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: CreateObjective
    C->>A: CreateObjective(parentId, title)
    A->>PM: CreateObjective(parentId, title)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PA-->>PM: []LifeTheme
    PM->>PM: Find parent (theme ID or objective ID via tree-walk)
    PM->>PM: Append new Objective to parent
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>PA: ensureThemeIDs() [generate objective ID]
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(themes.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM->>PA: GetThemes() [re-read for generated ID]
    PM-->>A: *Objective
    A-->>C: *Objective (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: UpdateObjective
    C->>A: UpdateObjective(objectiveId, title, tags)
    A->>PM: UpdateObjective(objectiveId, title, tags)
    PM->>PM: validateTags(tags) [trim, dedup]
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findObjectiveByID() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Update title & tags on found objective
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: DeleteObjective
    C->>A: DeleteObjective(objectiveId)
    A->>PM: DeleteObjective(objectiveId)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findObjectiveParent() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Remove objective from parent slice
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: SetObjectiveStatus
    C->>A: SetObjectiveStatus(objectiveId, status)
    A->>PM: SetObjectiveStatus(objectiveId, status)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findObjectiveByID() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: validateOKRStatusTransition(current, new)
    PM->>PM: [if completing] Check all children completed/archived
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: CloseObjective
    C->>A: CloseObjective(objectiveId, closingStatus, closingNotes)
    A->>PM: CloseObjective(objectiveId, closingStatus, closingNotes)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findObjectiveByID() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Verify objective is active
    PM->>PM: Set status=completed, closingStatus, closingNotes, closedAt
    PM->>PM: Auto-close all active child KRs
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: ReopenObjective
    C->>A: ReopenObjective(objectiveId)
    A->>PM: ReopenObjective(objectiveId)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findObjectiveByID() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Verify objective is completed
    PM->>PM: Clear status, closingStatus, closingNotes, closedAt
    PM->>PM: Reopen all completed child KRs
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
